<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> give oneself a shot in the arm • shoot oneself in the foot</xh5><p> <i>give oneself a shot in the arm—</i>inject oneself with a drug: The next day I got enough courage to do it myself and I <u>gave myself a shot in the arm</u>. The needle did not hurt going in... <i>shoot onself in the foot—</i>act against one’s own interest: You’re <u>shooting yourself in the foot</u> if you use the “can’t afford the time” excuse. In reality, you can’t afford not to.</p> </entry>
